The air became thick with arrows and then she could see nothing more.  A thud was heard as she fell to the ground from her horse. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 441<br> <font color=#993300>(8/23/01 3:51:40 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Arrows</span><hr size=1> Hipp growled as the arrows began flying by....then she heard Alcippe's gasping voice and spun her horse around. She raced to the young woman's side and jumped off her mare ..flying to her side.  Quickly, she picked her up into her arms...&quot;Hold on, Alcippe..hold on.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udelilahtragedy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delilah Tragedy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#993300>(8/23/01 3:55:32 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A shot from the woods</span><hr size=1> She saw the first fallen Amazon. Eyes wide, she looked up to see the sky filled with arrows. Her tiger had seen this and oddly enough.. it's fur turned into a sort of metal. She had never seen her tiger do this, but she had no time to waste. She had no time to wonder where the first fallen was still alive. She yelled to the other amazons, &quot;ROLIO EZO!&quot; Watch out.. the arrows were beginning to shower down oddly. It didn't seem that the archers where in any particular allignment. This was good. She dodged a couple of arrows and her sword helped in blocking some.<br>
<br>
&quot;POLEMOS KLAIO!!!!&quot; she shouted loudly. The shower of arrows was lessening as she spotted Saurian warriors emerging from the forest....<br>
